{"tid":120381,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"其實係咪好on9?","createTime":"2017-02-14T11:38:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T14:16:54.000Z","uid":21910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"11ca8587822a5bf215c2d77c89eaad63ae40f3d7","tid":120381,"uid":21910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:38:41.000Z","msg":"一直識個女仔十幾年 斷斷續續咁聯絡<br />\n由小學到依家20幾歲  都好難鐘意其他人  十幾年黎 仲算唔同中學 但都係對佢念念不忘<br />\n一路都好似只係我揾佢only但有時我都唔識分係咪hea覆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n 有時又會幾多野講 但會feel 到fd zone 左  個陣佢又會講下佢bf d 野，所以早幾年都諗住算數 但呢1,2 年又撞番佢  無意中知道佢地散左 令到我又再囉囉攣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  其實我係咪太on9 ?<br />\n一直執著係到？ 希望巴絲屌醒我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a827ad2b4e3e95730a7ce1326ec8f31bddbb6ad","tid":120381,"uid":21910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T11:49:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43623f5177d6695e49e0e25276172b7b0b5565b","tid":120381,"uid":21910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:09:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4076614d81cdcd60219f3e3f9b176fdd3caf68e4","tid":120381,"uid":41638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:28:51.000Z","msg":"on9"},{"pid":"9f0a07ac5a1a5efa2e041a387ddced1e168b73dc","tid":120381,"uid":8081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:29:58.000Z","msg":"巴打同我一樣咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b98dfd3273df1975dc7d212a792ab3a3e05f1fe","tid":120381,"uid":21910,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T12:30:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>巴打同我一樣咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你又點解咁on9<img src=\"